INSERT INTO `pages` VALUES (1,'The Yenching Academy brings our students rich history and culture as well as real-time development of China. As a prestigious college within Peking University, the Yenching Academy prepares a diverse group of international and Chinese students for tackling the most challenging issues facing the world.',1,0,'THE YENCHING ACADEMY'),(2,'Peking University has been at the forefront of Chinas modernization and \nsocial progress since 1898.\nPeking University (PKU) is one of the most prestigious institutions of higher education in China and its history of promoting social progress and strong academic tradition extends over a century.\nPKU WebSite\nLEADERSHIP\nMESSAGE FROM THE LEADERSHIP\nMISSION\n',1,1,'ABOUT PKU'),(3,'The Yenching Academy has assembled an acclaimed advisory board made up of scholars and thought leaders with strong focus in China. Our advisory board provides strong support to future global leaders.\nDeans\nInternational Advisory Board\nInternational Academic Advisory Council',1,2,'LEADERSHIP'),(4,'Message from the President\nThe Yenching Academy, the most ambitious academic initiative Peking University has launched since the turn of the new century, is dedicated to fostering an environment of learning and research that addresses the need for knowledge, ideas, moral character, and human understanding in the age of diversity, respect, and cooperation. The Yenching Scholars, young talents from across the world, will make the world an ever better place.\nMessage from the Dean\nThe Yenching Academy is a prestigious college within Peking University. As the focal point of innovative research in the areas of humanities and social sciences, and academic and cultural engagement between its scholars, faculty, and prominent political, business, and thought leaders from across the globe, the Yenching Academy is more than just an academic institution, but rather an idea incubator- cultivating the leaders who will make a positive impact on the world.',1,3,'MESSAGE FROM THE LEADERSHIP'),(5,'To provide an elite \nChinese Studies experience.\nThe Yenching Academy provides an extraordinary education experience that draws from western and eastern perspectives; cultivates leaders who will advocate for global progress and cultural understanding.',1,4,'MISSION'),(6,'The first-of-its-kind Chinese Studies program holds in mainland China.\n\nThe Yenching Academy offers a 1-year Master of Chinese Studies program (in English) designed to prepare an elite class of future leaders to meet the challenges of the 21st century global landscape.',2,0,'PROGRAM'),(7,'The inaugural class of 100 Yenching Scholars will begin in the September of 2015. Yenching Scholars will comprise of a diverse group of talented young leaders who demonstrate academic excellence, leadership, innovative thought, and a commitment to the betterment of society.\nYenching Scholars will reflect the richness of culture and academic, religious, ethnic, and socio-economic diversity represented across the globe.\nAs Yenching Scholars is a highly competitive masters program, applicants must possess excellent academic backgrounds and personal statements and extracurricular activities that highlight a passion for social engagement and service. Applicants should also have a demonstrated ability to conduct independent research in a particular field.\nSCHOLARSHIPS\nYenching Scholars receive a full tuition scholarship, accommodation in the residential college, and a stipend to cover living expenses.\nVISA INFORMATION\nUpon acceptance into Yenching Academy, scholars who are non-Chinese nationals must apply for a Chinese student visa.\nThe Yenching Academy Administration Office and Office of International Relations at Peking University will assist you in this process and ensure that you have all the proper documentation. Please visit the Office of International Relations at Peking University here for more information.',2,1,'ADMISSIONS'),(8,'The Yenching Academy has a dedicated Career Development and Alumni Services Office, which will guide scholars in their career planning and aid in career training and placement throughout their year at Yenching, as well as when they join the Peking University alumni network around the world.',2,2,'CAREER DEVELOPMENT & \nALUMNI SERVICES'),(9,'20: internationally reputed academic luminaries\n30: most renowned and influential PKU scholars\n20: visiting senior fellows with worldwide recognition\nThe Yenching Academy faculty is an esteemed group comprised of pioneering researchers and practitioners with a diversity of academic backgrounds, research expertise, and experience. They come from a wide range of countries that span across the globe and are passionate about making a positive global impact and dedicated to teaching and research excellence.',2,3,'FACULTY'),(10,'All students of the Yenching Academy will be Yenching Scholars.\nYenching Scholars not only engage in and develop their own learning experiences, but also work with the pioneers in their field to develop and apply innovative research in the areas of humanities and social sciences.\nThis Chinese Studies program integrates interdisciplinary approaches, pluralistic perspectives, and cutting-edge research to equip scholars with a rich understanding of Chinese Studies. Scholars will also build on this rich understanding by gaining expertise in one of six concentrations.\nConcentrations\nLiterature and Culture\nHistory and Archaeology\nPhilosophy and Religion\nPublic Policy and International Relations\nEconomics and Management aw and Society',2,4,'THE PROGRAM'),(11,'As a former Imperial Garden, the idyllic Jing-Yuan Courtyard is the focal point of student life.\n\nThe Yenching Academy is located at the Jing-Yuan Courtyard on the Peking University campus. Within the premise of the Jing-Yuan Courtyard, 6 historical buildings in the Courtyard will be renovated to provide state-of-the-art teaching and learning facilities. Yenching Scholars will live, learn, collaborate, and engage in an exclusive community of scholars.',3,0,NULL);
/*!40000 ALTER TABLE `pages` ENABLE KEYS */;
